## Helm Charts

### Library Chart (_lib/service)
All services use the shared library chart at `k8s/helm/{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/_lib/service/`.
It provides:
- Deployment (with security contexts, health checks, resource limits)
- Service (ClusterIP)
- ServiceAccount
- Ingress (optional, Traefik)
- HPA (optional)
- PDB (optional)
- RBAC (optional){{ if hasItem .Project.Spec.Infrastructure.Components "dapr" }}
- Dapr Subscriptions (optional){{ end }}

### Adding Values
```yaml
services:
  my-service:
    enabled: true
    replicas: 2
    env:
      CUSTOM_VAR: value
    secrets:
      - my-secret
```

### Image Registry
- Local (k3d): `{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/SERVICE_NAME:latest`
{{ if eq .Project.Spec.Cloud.Provider "gcp" }}- Staging: `{{ .Project.Spec.Cloud.Region }}-docker.pkg.dev/{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}-staging/{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/SERVICE_NAME:TAG`
- Production: `{{ .Project.Spec.Cloud.Region }}-docker.pkg.dev/{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}-production/{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/SERVICE_NAME:TAG`{{ end }}
{{ if eq .Project.Spec.Cloud.Provider "aws" }}- ECR: `ACCOUNT.dkr.ecr.{{ .Project.Spec.Cloud.Region }}.amazonaws.com/{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/SERVICE_NAME:TAG`{{ end }}
